{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"难道他不知道吗？当坟中的朽骨被揭发，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"胸中的秘密被显示的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"在那日，他们的主，确是彻知他们的。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"大难，"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"大难是什么，"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你怎能知道大难是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"在那日, 众人将似分散的飞蛾，"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"山岳将似疏松的采绒。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"至于善功的分量较重者，"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"将在满意的生活中；"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"至于善功的分量较轻者，"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"他的归宿是深坑。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"你怎能知道深坑里有什么？"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"有烈火。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"竞赛富庶, 已使你们疏忽，"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"直到你们去游坟地。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"真的, 你们将来就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"真的, 你们将来就知道了。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"真的, 假若你们有真知灼见, (你们必不疏忽)，"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你们必定看见火狱，"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"然后，你们必亲眼看见它。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日，你们必为恩泽而被审问。"},{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以时光盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"人确是在亏折之中，"},{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"惟信道而且行善，并以真理相劝，以坚忍相勉的人则不然。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"伤哉！每个诽谤者，诋毁者，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他聚积财产, 而当作武器，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他以为他的财产，能使他不灭。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"绝不然，他必定要被投在毁灭坑中。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你怎能知道毁灭坑是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"是安拉的燃着的烈火。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"能升到人的心上。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他们必定要被关在烈火中，"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"吊在许多高柱子上。"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"难道你不知道你的主怎样处治象的主人吗？"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"难道他没有使他们的计谋，变成无益的吗？"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他曾派遣成群的鸟去伤他们，"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"以粘土石射击他们，"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"使他们变成吃剩的干草一样。"},{"SurahNumber":106,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"因为保护古来氏，"},{"SurahNumber":106,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"因为在冬季和夏季的旅行中保护他们，"},{"SurahNumber":106,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"故教他们崇敬这天房的主，"},{"SurahNumber":106,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他曾为饥荒而赈济他们，曾为恐怖而保佑他们。"},{"SurahNumber":107,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你曾见否认报应日的人吗？"},{"SurahNumber":107,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他就是那个呵斥孤儿，"},{"SurahNumber":107,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"且不勉励人赈济贫民的人。"},{"SurahNumber":107,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"伤哉！礼拜的人们，"},{"SurahNumber":107,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"他们是疏忽拜功的，"},{"SurahNumber":107,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他们是沽名钓誉的，"},{"SurahNumber":107,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他们是不肯借人什物的。"},{"SurahNumber":108,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我确赐你多福，"},{"SurahNumber":108,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"故你应当为你的主而礼拜，并宰牺牲。"},{"SurahNumber":108,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"怨恨你者, 确是绝后的。"},{"SurahNumber":109,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你说：“不信道的人们啊！”"},{"SurahNumber":109,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"我不崇拜你们所崇拜的。"},{"SurahNumber":109,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你们也不崇拜我所崇拜的；"},{"SurahNumber":109,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"我不会崇拜你们所崇拜的，"},{"SurahNumber":109,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你们也不会崇拜我所崇拜的；"},{"SurahNumber":109,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你们有你们的宗教，我有我的宗教。”"},{"SurahNumber":110,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当安拉的援助和胜利降临，"},{"SurahNumber":110,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"当你看见众人成群结队地崇奉安拉的宗教时，"},{"SurahNumber":110,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你应当赞颂你的主超绝万物，并且向他求饶，他确是至宥的。"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"愿焰父两手受伤！他必定受伤，"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他的财产，和他所获得的，将无裨于他，"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他将入有焰的烈火，"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他的担柴的妻子，也将入烈火，"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"她的颈上系着一条坚实的棕绳。"},{"SurahNumber":112,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你说：“他是安拉，是独一的主；"},{"SurahNumber":112,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"安拉是万物所仰赖的；"},{"SurahNumber":112,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他未生育， 也未被生育。"},{"SurahNumber":112,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"没有任何物可以做他的匹敌。”"},{"SurahNumber":113,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你说：“我求庇于曙光的主，"},{"SurahNumber":113,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"免遭他所创造者的毒害；"},{"SurahNumber":113,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"免遭黑夜笼罩时的毒害；"},{"SurahNumber":113,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"免遭吹破坚决的主意者的毒害；"},{"SurahNumber":113,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"免遭嫉妒者嫉妒时的毒害。”"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你说：“我求庇于世人的养主，"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"世人的君主，"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"世人的主宰，"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"免遭潜伏的教唆者的毒害，"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"他在世人的胸中教唆，"},{"SurahNumber":114,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他是属于精灵和人类的。"}]}